  "info": {
    "contact": {
      "name": "VEVO Projects",
      "email": "VEVO.Projects@homeaffairs.gov.au"
    },
    "description": "This API allows authorised Australian Organisations to perform a Entitlement check for a Visa Holder.\n\nThe API is a modernised version of [Visa Entitlement Verification Online (VEVO) for Organisations](https://immi.homeaffairs.gov.au/visas/already-have-a-visa/check-visa-details-and-conditions/check-conditions-online/for-organisations) Web Service.\n\n### Operations:\n\nThis API exposes the following operations:\n\n* `HEAD /visa/v1/entitlements` - Perform a system health check.\n* `POST /visa/v1/entitlements/checks` - Conduct a Visa Entitlement Checks\n\n### Authentication\n\nUsers of this API must be enrolled via the [Home Affairs Access Manager](https://am.homeaffairs.gov.au) and will be authorised to retrieve one or more categories of Visa Entitlement data.\nEach API Request **must** include the following HTTP Headers:\n\n* `Authorization`:\n  * set to `Bearer {access_token}`. \n  * Access Tokens are obtained from our OAuth 2.0 provider, details below.\n  * Tokens are valid for 8 hours and may be used multiple times in that timeframe.\n* `x-api-key`:\n  * Set this to the clientId generated during Home Affairs Access Manager machine certificate registration.\n\n### Error Handling\n\n* This API returns appropriate HTTP status codes and error responses for a range of failure scenarios.\n* If you encounter an undocumented exception please get in touch with the Department using the contact details below.\n\n\n### Rate Limiting\n\n* Rate limiting is applied and enforced to prevent excessive use or abuse of Departmental systems.\n* A `429` Status Code is returned if the rate limit is exceeded. \n* You may check your remaining request allowance by checking the `X-RateLimit-Limit` response header.\n\n### Logging and Auditing\n\n* All API requests and operations are logged for auditing and monitoring purposes.\n",
    "title": "(Visa) Entitlements",
    "version": "1.0.34",
    "x-ibm-name": "visa-entitlements"
  },
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "entitlements",
      "description": "Visa Entitlement operations"
    }
  ],
